@ClaudeWithDotNetSDK.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5290

### Health check
GET {{ClaudeWithDotNetSDK.Api_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### Blocking ask
POST {{ClaudeWithDotNetSDK.Api_HostAddress}}/api/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Prompt": "In one sentence: what is dependency injection?",
  "System": "You are a senior .NET engineer. Be blunt and concise."
}

###

### Streaming ask (open in browser or curl --no-buffer)
GET {{ClaudeWithDotNetSDK.Api_HostAddress}}/api/ask/stream?prompt=List+3+.NET+10+features+for+backend+developers
Accept: text/event-stream

###

### Tool use — order status
POST {{ClaudeWithDotNetSDK.Api_HostAddress}}/api/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Prompt": "What is the status of order ORD-1234?",
  "System": null
}

###
